{"tid":1181961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"召集所有有用開twitter嘅反送中巴絲 #antiELABhk","createTime":"2019-06-01T22:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T05:35:52.000Z","uid":33432,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d1b5d9910cbca33d77668fe31400dc4186806d7d","tid":1181961,"uid":33432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T22:29:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的，留意到有位熱心巴打開咗個咁嘅活動<br />\n<br />\n[反送中] #antiELABhk campaign<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1179897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1179897</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n於是就上咗twitter搵吓#antiELABhk呢個tag，竟然只係得一個tweet有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都就嚟9號，個白宮聯署就14號到期，只係喺香港人之間宣傳我諗已經唔係太夠... 各位有用開twitter嘅巴絲，不如我哋都加入埋呢個campaign啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家誠邀各位巴絲出tweet講吓反送中嘅嘢，講完落個tag #antiELABhk <br />\n呢幾日最好加埋白宮聯署嘅link啦，就嚟夠數㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n身在外地嘅巴絲，如果你哋身處嘅地方母語唔係中/英語，歡迎用埋當地語言，同你哋當地嘅朋友介紹返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有巴絲玩開另外任何其他社交平台都用得呢個tag，麻煩開埋post呼籲吓啦，遍地開花就靠每一個香港人參與喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3519d78a8027b727244c00ce3f4ad63bf030f2e","tid":1181961,"uid":140021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T22:53:09.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"fcf5a733b8e53a8de733180950a2c923c015578d","tid":1181961,"uid":33432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T22:53:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beee53b572d8cbb56142e13258117418cac9bd43","tid":1181961,"uid":140021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T22:54:38.000Z","msg":"更正返，係#antiELAB，無hk"},{"pid":"738f3e5fe893